
ebnf2ps.tar.gz contains the following files:

   README	this file
   ebnf-anb.el	ABNF parser
   ebnf-bnf.el	EBNF parser
   ebnf-dtd.el	DTD parser
   ebnf-ebx.el	EBNFX parser
   ebnf-iso.el	ISO EBNF parser
   ebnf-otz.el	EBNF optimizer
   ebnf-yac.el	Yacc/Bison parser
   ebnf2ps.el	main file
   ebnf2ps.new	News

The file iso-14977.pdf contains the ISO EBNF specification, this file is apart
from this package and it can be downloaded from:
http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/~mgk25/iso-14977.pdf

The file rfc2234.txt contains the ABNF specification, this file is apart from
this package and it can be downloaded from: http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2234.txt
or http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc2234.html, http://www.rnp.br/ietf/rfc/rfc2234.txt
(Augmented BNF for Syntax Specifications: ABNF).



Happy hacking


